    Aracnia steps forward to stand in between Megatron and Kitkat. "I came, I 
want to know whats going on after all. So, I guess you heard Megtron?"
    He gave a quizzical look, "Know what?" And then steped back, to give 
himself a little room.
    "Our council....Kitkat can explain better thant I can." She said, and 
turned to look at Kitkat.

    Nighteyes fell as the ship rocked. She had to find that spark...but 
suddenly looked up to see a clone of Megatron. What an odd surprize....
